description:
&lt;p&gt;We now need a highly motivated and experienced pharmacist with experience of secondary care high cost drugs to join the “in hospital care commissioning team” based in Exeter to take forward our high cost drug strategy .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main priorities of this role will beto provide highly specialist advice to support commissioning of high cost, specialist medicines to ensure high quality patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will ensure providers, encompassed within the STP identify, plan and deliver maximum efficiency in the use of high cost medicines to deliver maximum benefit to the patient population.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about this vacancy please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;John Finn&lt;/p&gt;
